## 4. Four Main Collecting Highlights\par
\par
### 4.1 The Mind Stone\par
\par
The Mind Stone is a major collectible card in the set and appears in three versions:\par
\par
1. Main set version.\par
   - Artwork by Volkan Baga.\par
   - Available in non-foil and traditional foil.\par
   - Found in both Play Boosters and Collector Boosters.\par
\par
2. Borderless Gauntlet version.\par
   - Shows the stone with Thanos imagery.\par
   - Traditional foil only.\par
   - Found only in Collector Boosters.\par
\par
3. Textless cosmic foil version.\par
   - Ultra-limited Marvel collectible.\par
   - Fewer than 150 copies printed.\par
   - Found only in Collector Boosters of any language.\par
   - Always English.\par
\par
### 4.2 Borderless Classic Comic Cards\par
\par
- Borderless classic comic cards use historic Marvel comic artwork on new-to-Magic legendary creature cards.\par
- These cards are positioned as premium collectibles and potential Commander centerpiece cards.\par
- There are 15 mythic rare classic comic cards.\par
- 4 of the classic comic cards are double-faced cards.\par
- They are traditional foil only.\par
- They are found only in Collector Boosters.\par
- They can appear in Collector Boosters of any language, but the cards themselves are always English.\par
\par
### 4.3 Borderless Source Material Cards\par
\par
- Borderless source material cards combine Marvel comic artwork with Magic reprints.\par
- Featured Marvel artists include names such as Jack Kirby, Alex Ross, Dan Adkins, and Tony S. Daniel.\par
- This category includes source material versions of legendary creatures from Secret Lair\u8217?s Marvel Superdrop.\par
- There are 60 source material cards.\par
- Three of the 60 are different versions of Heroic Intervention.\par
- Source material cards have equal appearance rates within the source material card pool.\par
- A non-foil source material card replaces a common in roughly 1 in 24 Play Boosters.\par
- Every Collector Booster contains one non-foil or traditional foil source material card.\par
\par
### 4.4 Borderless Logo Cards\par
\par
- Borderless logo cards use stylized Marvel character art on monocolor backgrounds with character logos.\par
- They appear on legendary creatures from across the set.\par
- There are 15 rare logo cards and 13 mythic rare logo cards.\par
- They appear in non-foil and traditional foil versions.\par
- They can be found in Play Boosters and Collector Boosters.\par
\par
