## 5. Booster Fun Treatments and Collectible Card Categories\par
\par
### 5.1 Borderless Scene Cards\par
\par
- Scene cards combine to form larger Marvel artwork scenes.\par
- They can be collected for decks, binders, display, or gameplay.\par
- There are six scenes available from cards found in Play Boosters and Collector Boosters:\par
  - A 4-card Fantastic Four scene by Leinil Francis Yu and Sunny Gho.\par
  - A 4-card Daredevil vs. Hell\u8217?s Kitchen foes scene by Kev Walker.\par
  - A 6-card Captain America vs. HYDRA scene by Annie Wu.\par
  - A 6-card gamma-themed confrontation scene by Adi Granov.\par
  - An 18-card cosmic cube battle scene by Johan Grenier.\par
  - A 5-card meal-sharing scene by Chris Bachalo, formed from the front faces of double-sided scene cards.\par
- Scene cards in Play Boosters and Collector Boosters include:\par
  - 3 commons.\par
  - 12 uncommons.\par
  - 8 rares.\par
  - 15 mythic rares.\par
- Scene cards appear in non-foil and traditional foil in Play Boosters and Collector Boosters.\par
- There are two Scene Boxes, and each Scene Box contains 6 traditional foil new-to-Magic borderless scene cards.\par
- Non-foil versions of Scene Box scene cards appear in Collector Boosters.\par
\par
### 5.2 Borderless Lands\par
\par
- The set introduces five new rare dual lands.\par
- Each rare dual land has a borderless version showing the location through an Avengers computer-screen style treatment.\par
- There are 5 rare borderless lands.\par
- They appear in non-foil and traditional foil versions in Play Boosters and Collector Boosters.\par
\par
### 5.3 Showcase Panel Cards\par
\par
- Showcase panel cards use a comic-panel-inspired frame.\par
- They highlight major Marvel objects, stories, and moments.\par
- Examples include Mj\u246?lnir, Hammer of Thor and Armor Wars.\par
- There are 11 rare showcase panel cards and 6 mythic rare showcase panel cards.\par
- They appear in non-foil and traditional foil versions in Play Boosters and Collector Boosters.\par
\par
### 5.4 Full-Art City Calm and City Chaos Basic Lands\par
\par
The set includes two full-art basic land cycles:\par
\par
- City calm basic lands: quieter moments featuring Super Heroes in calmer city settings.\par
- City chaos basic lands: action-focused city scenes across Marvel locations.\par
\par
Availability by product:\par
\par
| Product | Basic land treatment availability |\par
|---|---|\par
| Play Boosters | Non-foil and traditional foil city calm and city chaos basics |\par
| Collector Boosters | Traditional foil city calm and city chaos basics |\par
| Jumpstart Boosters | 1 non-foil city calm or city chaos basic per booster |\par
| Bundles | 1 non-foil and 1 traditional foil city chaos basic of each type |\par
| Gift Bundles | 1 non-foil and 1 traditional foil city calm basic of each type |\par
| Collector\u8217?s Edition Commander Decks | Surge foil city calm and city chaos basics |\par
| Beginner Boxes | Non-foil city calm and city chaos basics |\par
