## 6. Product Details\par
\par
## 6.1 Play Boosters\par
\par
A Play Booster box contains 30 Play Boosters.\par
\par
Each Play Booster contains:\par
\par
- 14 Magic cards.\par
- 1 helper card or double-sided token.\par
\par
### Play Booster card slot structure\par
\par
| Slot | Contents / notes |\par
|---|---|\par
| 7 common slots | Main set commons; scene cards may appear; source material card can replace a common in about 1 in 24 boosters. |\par
| 3 uncommon slots | Main set uncommons; uncommon scene cards can appear. |\par
| 1 wildcard slot | Can be common, uncommon, rare, or mythic rare; can include main set cards, scene cards, logo cards, panel cards, and rare borderless lands. |\par
| 1 rare/mythic slot | Main set rare/mythic, scene card, logo card, or panel card. |\par
| 1 traditional foil slot | Foil card of any rarity; can include main set cards, scene cards, logo cards, panel cards, or borderless land. |\par
| 1 land slot | Can be common dual land, default-frame basic land, city calm basic, or city chaos basic, in non-foil or traditional foil. |\par
| 1 helper/token slot | Non-foil helper card or double-sided token. |\par
\par
### Play Booster key counts and rates\par
\par
- Common slots:\par
  - 81 main-set commons are available in the common slots.\par
  - 3 common scene cards appear in the common slots at an 8.6% rate.\par
  - A non-foil source material card replaces a common in 1 out of 24 Play Boosters.\par
- Uncommon slots:\par
  - 100 main-set uncommons are available in the uncommon slots.\par
  - 12 uncommon scene cards appear in the uncommon slots at a 12% rate.\par
- Wildcard slot:\par
  - Main set common: 12.4%.\par
  - Main set uncommon: 64%.\par
  - Main set rare: 16.8%.\par
  - Main set mythic rare: 2.1%.\par
  - Uncommon scene card: 2.7%.\par
  - Rare borderless land: 1%.\par
  - Other wildcard possibilities include lower-rate common/rare/mythic scene cards, rare/mythic logo cards, and rare/mythic panel cards.\par
- Rare/mythic slot:\par
  - Main set rare: 76.1%.\par
  - Main set mythic rare: 16.6%.\par
  - Rare scene card: 1%.\par
  - Mythic rare scene card: 0.8%.\par
  - Rare logo card: 2.4%.\par
  - Mythic rare logo card: 0.7%.\par
  - Rare panel card: 1.9%.\par
  - Mythic rare panel card: less than 1%.\par
- Traditional foil slot:\par
  - Main set common: 59.9%.\par
  - Main set uncommon: 29.6%.\par
  - Main set rare: 5.9%.\par
  - Main set mythic rare: 1.2%.\par
  - Uncommon scene card: 1.2%.\par
  - Other foil possibilities include low-rate scene, logo, panel, and borderless land cards.\par
- Land slot:\par
  - Non-foil common dual land: 40%.\par
  - Traditional foil common dual land: 10%.\par
  - Non-foil default-frame basic land: 20%.\par
  - Traditional foil default-frame basic land: 5%.\par
  - Non-foil city calm basic land: 10%.\par
  - Traditional foil city calm basic land: 2.5%.\par
  - Non-foil city chaos basic land: 10%.\par
  - Traditional foil city chaos basic land: 2.5%.\par
- Helper/token slot:\par
  - Non-foil helper card: 8.5%.\par
  - Double-sided token: 91.5%.\par
\par
Note for simulations: Play Boosters in this set do contain lands in the land slot, including common dual lands and multiple types of basic lands.\par
