## 6.2 Collector Boosters\par
\par
A Collector Booster box contains 12 Collector Boosters.\par
\par
Each Collector Booster contains:\par
\par
- 15 Magic cards.\par
- 1 art card or traditional foil double-sided token.\par
\par
### Collector Booster card slot structure\par
